---
title: Mumbai White Fish & Bengali Coconut Sauce with Honey-Roasted Veggies & Mixed Leaf Salad
description: A fresh cut of fish is so refreshing, but how about darkening the taste with some delicious Mumbai spice and a
coconutty Bengali sauce drizzled on top? It won’t disappoint and might even become a new fish favourite!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/651a249cbbf22188bdeceba3-ac323f2b.jpeg
